    <item>
      <title>Be flexible</title>
      <link>https://linguage.github.io/terencetao/career-advice/orig/be-flexible/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 May 2007 19:02:56 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://linguage.github.io/terencetao/career-advice/orig/be-flexible/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://linguage.github.io/terencetao/career-advice/zh/be-flexible.zh/&#34;&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;div&#xA;  class=&#34;link-card group relative my-3 w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-[var(--lc-border,rgba(15,23,42,0.12))] bg-[var(--lc-bg,var(--card-bg,var(--surface,#ffffff))))] transition-shadow duration-150 hover:shadow-[var(--lc-shadow-hover,0_14px_30px_-18px_rgba(15,23,42,0.35))]&#34;&#xA;  data-url=&#34;https://terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/be-flexible/&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a&#xA;    class=&#34;link-card__fallback block px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--lc-url,var(--link-color,#0e6a85))] underline-offset-4 hover:underline&#34;&#xA;    href=&#34;https://terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/be-flexible/&#34;&#xA;    target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xA;    rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;  &gt;&#xA;    https://terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/be-flexible/&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#34;be-flexible&#34;&gt;Be flexible&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;It is not the strongest of the species that survives, nor the most intelligent, but the one most responsive to change.&#xA;(Leon C. Megginson)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Mathematical research is by its nature unpredictable – if we knew in advance what the answer would be and how to do it, it wouldn&amp;rsquo;t be research! You should therefore be prepared for research to lead you in unexpected directions, and it may end up that you may find a new problem or area of mathematics more interesting than the one you were initially working in. (See also &amp;ldquo;Don&amp;rsquo;t be afraid to learn things outside your field&amp;rdquo; and &amp;ldquo;Learn the power of other mathematician&amp;rsquo;s tools&amp;rdquo;.)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
